'''妮娜·阿里安达'''（{{lang-en|Nina Arianda}}；{{bd|1984年|9月18日|||catIdx=A阿里安达}}）是美国女演员。

==生平==
1984年9月18日，妮娜·阿里安达出生在[[美国|美国]][[纽约市|纽约市]][[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]]。<ref name=PB1>{{cite web|last=Blank|first=Matthew|title=Born Yesterday Tony Nominee Nina Arianda|url=http://www.playbill.com/celebritybuzz/article/151568-PLAYBILLCOMS-CUE-A-Born-Yesterday-Tony-Nominee-Nina-Arianda|website=Playbill|date=2011-06-07|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111217235729/http://www.playbill.com/celebritybuzz/article/151568-PLAYBILLCOMS-CUE-A-Born-Yesterday-Tony-Nominee-Nina-Arianda|archive-date=2011-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>她的父母是出生在[[德国|德国]]的[[乌克兰|乌克兰]]人。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/19/magazine/nina-arianda-venus-in-fur.html|title=Nina Arianda Is Fueling Fantasies|first=Andrew|last=Goldman|work=The New York Times|date=2012-02-17|accessdate=2021-01-30|archive-date=2019-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190501082806/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/19/magazine/nina-arianda-venus-in-fur.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2011/11/07/the-natural-john-lahr |title=The Natural |work=The New Yorker |access-date=2021-01-30 |archive-date=2019-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190501082852/https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2011/11/07/the-natural-john-lahr |dead-url=no }}</ref>她在[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]的克利夫顿和德国的[[海德堡|海德堡]]长大。2009年，她取得了[[新學院_(紐約)|新学院]]尤金·朗学院（{{lang|en|Eugene Lang College}}）的文学学士学位，以及纽约大学蒂希艺术学院（{{lang|en|Tisch School of The Arts}}）研究生表演课程的美术硕士学位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tisch.nyu.edu/object/2011_tony_nominations.html|title=Tisch alumni nominations at the 2011 Tony Awards|website=Tisch at New York University|access-date=2021-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110705114707/http://www.tisch.nyu.edu/object/2011_tony_nominations.html|archive-date=2011-07-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

